            <div type="edition">
                <note>This division into textparts and the incipits are taken from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">5</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="part" xml:id="part1">
                    <label>Part 1</label>
                    <ab type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">ክፍል። ፍኖቱስ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ትሕትና፡ ወየውሃት፡ ወአፍቅሮ፡ ቢጽ፡ ወኢያምዕዖ፡ እኍ፡ 
                        ወተፋቅሮ፡ ወሰላም፡ ምስለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="part" xml:id="part2">
                    <label>Part 2</label>
                    <ab type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">ክፍል። ተወከለ፡ ዳዊት፡ በእግዚአብሔር፡ ወኮኖ፡ ፀወነ፡ ወአድኃኖ፡ እምእደ፡ ሳኦል፡ ንጉሥ፡ 
                        ወዘአመ፡ ዮናታን፡ ወልዱ፡ ወዘአመ፡ ኢሎፍላውያን፡ ወዘአመ፡ አማላቃውያን፡ </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="part" xml:id="part3">
                    <label>Part 3</label>
                    <ab type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">ክፍል። ተዘከር፡ እስኩ፡ ስሞሙ፡ ለእለ፡ ገብርዋ፡ ለሠናይት፡ ወኢትርሳዕ፡ ምግባሪሆሙ፡ ወቅናዕ፡ ከመ፡ 
                        ይኩን፡ ስምከ፡ ከመ፡ ስመ፡ ዚአሆሙ፡ ከመ፡ በስማያት፡ ትትፈሣሕ፡ ምስለ፡ ዚአሆሙ፡</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
